Reported-by: Chen Zhongjin <chenzhongjin@huawei.com>
Signed-off-by: Rafael J. Wysocki <rafael.j.wysocki@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Chen Zhongjin <chenzhongjin@huawei.com>
